steps.name: Prep
steps.instruction: Remove and discard seeds from squash, then cut halves into quarters

steps.name: Cooking
steps.instruction: Place squash in large microwave-safe dish. Pour water over squash; cover and microwave on HIGH for 7–8 minutes or until tender, then uncover carefully and drain. Let stand until cool

steps.name: Cooking
steps.instruction: Combine honey, lemon juice, garam masala, and salt; whisk in oil
Place squash flesh-side up on serving platter; top each with 1/2 cup arugula and even amounts nuts, goat cheese, and pomegranate arils (if using)
Drizzle dressing over each squash salad; serve
